{"tid":1105019,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句好深印象嘅唐宋詩","createTime":"2019-04-13T14:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T22:58:21.000Z","uid":14459,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"08012febc2a2e30924f87c56c0efd72032189884","tid":1105019,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">積雨</span><span style=\"color: green;\">空林</span><span style=\"color: red;\">煙火遲</span><br />\n<br />\n出自王維嘅《積雨輞川莊作》<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">積雨</span>，猶久雨，連綿不絕嘅綿密雨勢<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">空林</span>，唔係直指個林乜人乜生物都冇，而係好似《山居秋暝》句「空山新雨後」咁係一個幽靜狀態<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">煙火遲</span>，農户炊煙裊裊上升，因為積雨關係，煙嘅升騰都有種遲滯嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n呢一句之精煉，完全體現到王維「詩中有畫，畫中有詩」嘅精髓。七隻字一隻不能少，加埋哂就係一幅濕淋淋嘅山水畫，成個大環境同個氛圍完全寫哂出嚟，我睇幾多次都係咁鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家都一齊分享下，同埋最好唔好係一隻詩而係一句詩啦，一隻同一句反映出嘅真係有唔同，有需要嘅都可以係一聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2975352ddd2807299fa6018c4013730da1452813","tid":1105019,"uid":140813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"事了拂衣去，深藏身與名。"},{"pid":"3ee02118059430712c9d279c256764f993adfcd3","tid":1105019,"uid":140813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2975352ddd2807299fa6018c4013730da1452813","tid":1105019,"uid":140813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"事了拂衣去，深藏身與名。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"李白《俠客行》"},{"pid":"06199f108bcbb4709f07ac6d7a7ac645df4ab7e0","tid":1105019,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冚家鏟"},{"pid":"fed861fc89f2bae13c9c1082f8c95b3c61f956bd","tid":1105019,"uid":198787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"相顧無